Key Points:\
\uc0\u9679 \
\uc0\u9679 \
\uc0\u9679 \
Asthma attacks happen because the small tubes in the lungs become too narrow.\
Muscle spasms and swelling plus mucus block airflow.\
Symptoms: coughing (often at night), wheezing (whistling breath sound), chest tightness,\
and trouble taking full breaths.\
Triggers: exercise (exercise-induced asthma), cold air, allergens (dust mites, pet dander,\
mold), smoke, or respiratory infections can trigger an attack. Sometimes stress or strong\
emotions can too.\
