Prevention: Some cancers can be prevented (avoid smoking, sun protection, vaccines for\
viruses like HPV). Healthy habits (diet, exercise) may lower some risks.\
Survival: Not all tumors are deadly. Many people survive cancer, especially when found early.\
Support from doctors, family, and healthy choices help.\
