transplant can last many years, but not forever.)More to Learn:\
Tissue donation: Besides organs, tissues like corneas (for vision), skin (for burns), and bone\
marrow (for blood diseases) can also be donated.\
Gift of life: Organ donation saves lives. Discussing donation wishes with family and registering\
as a donor can help others.\
